Rick Stein: From Venice to Istanbul - Series 1, Episode 5




Greek Peloponnese / Western Turkey

Rick Stein arrives in the Greek Peloponnese and samples memorable dishes like rooster stew hilopites with mizithra cheese and the best home-made moussaka he's ever had. He also enjoys an Aegean Beef Stew in the hilltop village of Sirince in Western Turkey. In his Symi island kitchen he cooks galaktoboureko, Greece's all-time favourite dessert.




Original Air Date: 04-Sep-2015
